{"tid":992620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★區諾軒：我係孟加拉人關你鬼事！派＄4000申請表「荒謬」","createTime":"2019-01-23T10:07:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T06:16:33.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"39296eac8884756b191f56a231f5431d97e26eed","tid":992620,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.linepost.hk/images/2019/01/j/190123.4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.linepost.hk%2Fimages%2F2019%2F01%2Fj%2F190123.4.jpg&h=b3328c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n區諾軒：派＄4000申請表「荒謬」<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒列出數個派＄4000申請表的「荒謬之處」，包括在「經濟活動身份」一欄，有就業、失業、料理家務者的選項，他質疑「申請人工作是甚麼關你乜事」，因不影響是否能夠獲得＄4000。<br />\n<br />\n「族裔」一欄，選項包括華人、尼泊爾人、泰國人等，區諾軒質疑，申請人屬何族裔，「關能否獲得＄4000有何關係，係咪我係孟加拉人人就無得攞？」強調只要是香港永久居民就可以領取，笑稱有申請人在「其他」一欄填「香港人」，認為搞笑至極。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zmPeY_ZM0QQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzmPeY_ZM0QQ&d=zxjdt1ahhBQFz5N%2FyWdJ%2Fm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=df2425c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zmPeY_ZM0QQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.linepost.hk/index.php/news/6944-j190123-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.linepost.hk%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2F6944-j190123-5&d=zxjdt1ahhBQFz5N%2FyWdJ%2Fm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9a16d8ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.linepost.hk/index.php/news/6944-j190123-5</a>"},{"pid":"8c0e29df8deff880d7299872afcf8367cf4fac2a","tid":992620,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:07:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65828c792e188efcc33007045a1cc59efceed8c","tid":992620,"uid":19454,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:08:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有申請人在「其他」一欄填「香港人」</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/n